      <UL>
      <LH>Parameters:</LH>
      <LI><I>AEditor</I> - identifies the undo/redo list owner</LI>
      <LI><I>RedoList</I> - when this instance is used as undo list, specify
      a redo list to allow clear it at each valid AddChange call</LI>
      </UL> }
